  {
    "step": 1,
    "subject": "Fellow Cal Bear 🚀 – Congrats on Finex’s Series B!",
    "body": "Hi Jane,\n\nI noticed you graduated from UC Berkeley – Go Bears! 🎉 Congratulations on Finex’s recent $50M Series B round – impressive growth. I’ve helped other fintech leaders at Berkeley alumni networks tighten their risk‑management pipelines using AI. Would love to share a quick 10‑minute call to see if there’s a fit.\n\nBest,\nAlex (LeadCraft AI)"
  },
  {
    "step": 2,
    "subject": "Finex’s new API suite – any integration challenges?",
    "body": "Hey Jane,\n\nFollowing up on my previous note – I saw Finex just launched a new API suite. Many of our Berkeley‑network clients faced integration hiccups and we helped streamline the process, shaving weeks off rollout time. If you’re open, I can share a brief case study.\n\nCheers,\nAlex"
  },
  {
    "step": 3,
    "subject": "Quick chat? – AI‑driven risk tools for Finex",
    "body": "Hi Jane,\n\nJust wanted to circle back in case my earlier messages slipped through. Our AI‑risk platform has already delivered a 20% reduction in false‑positive alerts for a fellow Berkeley fintech. Could we schedule a 15‑minute demo next week?\n\nThanks,\nAlex"
  }
]
